Bug #13016: Regression: Indicate continuations + cancellations

Bug #13016: Regression: Indicate continuations + cancellations
The web app doesn't show continuations properly. It should:
1.[x] In the routing results, only show icons for segments that are not continuations. 2.[x] In the trip details, similarly don't show a mode icon for continuations. The same test case also indicates that it doesn't show cancellations. It should:
1.[x] In the routing results, fade out trips that are cancelled 2.[x] In the routing results, don't give any badge groups which only have cancellations 3.[x] In the trip details, show a big banner indicating that a segment is cancelled 4.[ ] In the trip details, include a button to get alternative results
